            of the following taken into consideration;
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li>Disaster Recovery and Business Continuance</li>
            <li>Flexibility, Robustness, and Scalability</li>
            <li>Virtualization Infrastructure Design</li>
            <li>Application to Infrastructure Analysis and Design</li>
            <li>Network infrastructure Analysis and Design</li>
            <li>Global and Local Load Balancing Design</li>
